        ('Optimizing Your Content for Voice Queries', '<ul><li><strong>Target question keywords:</strong> Create content that directly answers "who," "what," "where," "when," "how," and "why" questions</li><li><strong>Use FAQ sections:</strong> Structured Q&A content is the #1 source for voice search answers</li><li><strong>Write conversationally:</strong> Match the natural language people use when speaking</li><li><strong>Aim for featured snippets:</strong> Concise, direct answers in 40-50 words are most likely to be read aloud by voice assistants</li><li><strong>Optimize for "near me" searches:</strong> Local business schema, Google Business Profile, and location-specific content</li></ul>'),
